author: Glink
description:
Outside Austin City Hall we met with Louis Rossmann and fellow activists known as "Clippys". Because it was removed from the agenda, the only 2 people allowed to speak on the public communications hearing were 2 representatives of LiveView Technologies (LVT), the agenda for item 33 has been delayed to December. Stay tuned to GTV for updates on this developing story.
